PrecisAuthorization for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to grant an EASEMENT [No. ES-957] to 938966 ONTARIO INC. (a wholly-owned subsidiary of Canril Corporation) encumbering, in perpetuity or for the term of the use of the works, some 4.5 hectares of land bordering Green's Creek on the south side of Innes Road near Blair, in the City of Gloucester, Ontario, for storm water management.
